19 July 2010Members of the media are invited to a photo opportunity of members of the Cabinet. This will take place before the commencement of the Cabinet Lekgotla which takes place on Tuesday, 20 July 2010 at the Presidential Guesthouse in Pretoria.The details are as follows:Date: Tuesday, 20 July 2010 Time: 09h00 for 09h30 Venue: Presidential Guesthouse in Pretoria (access through Gate 10)For confirmation of attendance, please email or sms your name, ID/passport number and the media house you represent to pheliswa@gcis.gov.za or 082 413 4609.For media enquiries contact:Bongiwe Gambu Cell: 082 714 9463Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)